cc:Work.dc:title: Tiger Head: Blood
cc:Work.dc:description: I suppose that might not be blood. Maybe the tiger just has a thing for cherry pie. And maybe it took a big old bite of cherry pie and then yawned. In that case it might not be blood. But I think it is blood, fresh kill.... ROAR! Synthesized and made bloody from a 1901 original. The article (although talking about another animal, but who cares!) had the scary quip "These animals, which kill their hundreds of people every year and slaughter many hundreds of cattle, roam about the open country and \ncarry terror to the settlements." ROAR!
